headline: Intuitive Surgical’s Cardiac Clearance Tests Valuation As da Vinci 5 Expands
summary: Intuitive Surgical received FDA clearance for its da Vinci 5 system in selected cardiac procedures, including mitral valve repair and cardiac revascularization. The approval enables minimally invasive approaches in areas of heart surgery that have traditionally relied on open procedures. The da Vinci 5 platform includes advanced imaging, smart instruments, and upgraded computing capabilities tailored to complex cardiac work.
